OL,3,CMemorial service held for mum shot
OL,4,Cdead on night out
OL,6,FFriends and relatives gathered at
OL,7,FSheffield Cathedral for a service held
OL,8,Fin memory of a young mother shot dead
OL,9,Fon a night out in the city.
OL,11,FShanice Brookes, 30, was a bystander
OL,12,Fwhen she was caught in crossfire
OL,13,Foutside the One Four One bar on West
OL,14,FStreet following an earlier
OL,15,Faltercation on 25 May.
OL,17,FShe died in hospital, leaving behind
OL,18,Fher 10-year-old son.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
