OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1783689573
OL,3,CMemorial service held for mum shot
OL,4,Cdead on night out
OL,6,FGuests were asked to wear bright
OL,7,Fcolours for Tuesday's service, led by
OL,8,FDean of Sheffield Abi Thompson.
OL,10,FThe song For Good, from the hit
OL,11,Fmusical Wicked, was played as part of
OL,12,Fthe tributes.
OL,14,FMs Brookes was a student at Sheffield
OL,15,FCollege and volunteered for the
OL,16,Fcommunity charity Zest.
OL,18,FIn a tribute following her death, her
OL,19,Ffamily described her as having "the
OL,20,Fbiggest heart and the kind of energy
OL,21,Fyou could never forget".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
