OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1783689573
OL,3,CMemorial service held for mum shot
OL,4,Cdead on night out
OL,6,FThe statement said: "She could light
OL,7,Fup every room she walked into with her
OL,8,Finfectious laugh, beautiful soul and
OL,9,Fmagical aura. Shanice made people feel
OL,10,Floved, safe and valued simply by being
OL,11,Fherself.
OL,13,F"She was truly one of a kind and she
OL,14,Fwill be missed by all who were lucky
OL,15,Fenough to know and love her."
OL,17,FJemele Rhone, 30, of Outram Road,
OL,18,FSheffield, has been charged with
OL,19,Fmurder. A provisional trial date is
OL,20,Fset for next January.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
